  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Grand Hotel Belvedere is on a Bed &amp; Breakfast basis, with a Half Board upgrade available at a supplement.</p>
<p>In the mornings a hot and cold buffet breakfast is served.</p>
<p>The Half Board upgrade comes with a five-course evening meal with a choice of main. With local produce, wild pickings and forever changing seasonal produce you will be serviced the most delicate meals as well as classic alpine dishes.</p>
<p>There are two contrasting bars within the hotel that are both open in the evening, with one serving specialty coffee in the morning too.</p>
<p><strong>No. of restaurants:</strong> 2</p>
<p><strong>Dress code for the restaurants:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Smart casual</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
