  <description><![CDATA[<p><span data-contrast="auto">The Grand Hotel Belvedere is Wengen's first five-star hotel. With an excellent location set back from the main street  you can enjoy the stunning Jungfrau views from the comfort of the hotels facilities. Check out the sun terrace for an afternoon drink, or unwind in the concrete style modern spa.</span></p>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Indulge within the tranquil settings</span></h3>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Reward yourself by coming back to the ultimate relaxation paradise after accomplishing an outdoor adventure. The iconic minimalist onsen style spa with heated indoor and outdoor pools, multiple saunas and Turkish steam bath makes the experience incredibly luxurious. Pamper yourself with spa treatments (payable locally), enjoy views of the Jungfrau from the outdoor pool or relax in the garden.</span></p>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">One-of-a-kind hotel</span></h3>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Dating back to 1912, this former Art Nouveau style hotel has been attractively renovated for September 2024. Bringing a traditional charm combined with modern architectural detail, it has a wooden feel and natural-coloured soft furnishings. The lobby and lounge areas are the perfect place to sit back and reflect and the spacious interiors have a light and airy atmosphere, with plenty of room choices to choose from. You can enjoy the picturesque views of the Jungfrau, Schilthorn, Silberhorn and Lauterbrunnen sights from the hotel's large glass panel windows.</span></p>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Fine dining</span></h3>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Offered on a bed &amp; breakfast basis, you can start the day with a filling and delicious breakfast, comprised of fresh fruit, pastries, hot servings and more. Upgrade to half board to complete the day with an astounding five-course meal with a choice of main, served within a relaxed atmosphere. Authentic dishes and local seasonal produce turn a meal into an experience. When looking for a bite to eat or a beverage to sip, the choice is yours with two bars and two restaurants. Treat yourself to a specialty coffee or slice of zigercake, or a bespoke cocktail on the terrace.</span></p>]]></description>
