  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Garden View Rooms</strong> are around 20-25m² and sleep two people with a bath or shower and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Jungfrau View Rooms</strong> are around 20-25m² and sleep two people with a bath or shower and WC. These rooms also have a south facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Garden View Rooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep two people with a bath or shower and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Jungfrau View Rooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep two people with a bath or shower and WC. These rooms also have a south facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite with Garden View</strong> are around 29m² and sleep two to three people and have a bathroom with a bathtub and WC. The third bed is a single sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite with Jungfrau View</strong> are around 29m² and sleep two to three people and have a bathroom with a bathtub and WC. The third bed is a single sofa bed. These rooms have a south facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea/coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF4.30 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged between six and 15 have a reduced fee of CHF2.00 per person per night. Children aged five years and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
